    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1901932/" class="title-link">从阿加马的“神圣的人”说起</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1901932"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/roada9m/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/roada9m/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
